{"tid":964033,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩動漫對白令你畢生難忘","createTime":"2019-01-01T03:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T15:57:52.000Z","uid":205704,"like":5,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":114,"replies":[{"pid":"9835c124a660d7a22ec015b5e083ce9ef2610eec","tid":964033,"uid":205704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T03:41:33.000Z","msg":"大家互相幫助，一起成功，一起幸福什麼的，不過是種理想。 <br />\n現實中，有人幸福，就必定有人被拋棄 <br />\n有人光鮮，就必須有人滿身泥濘。<br />\n<br />\n就係大老師教我睇化自己係邊緣人嘅事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43ba3558934d1339bc408654bb201f8c585dcde0","tid":964033,"uid":221571,"like":67,"dislike":4,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T03:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/APs3JxB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAPs3JxB.png&h=b618d01d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a15d4efb1388147ed8f94ecb55b7d69e2b934bba","tid":964033,"uid":205704,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"43ba3558934d1339bc408654bb201f8c585dcde0","tid":964033,"uid":221571,"like":67,"dislike":4,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T03:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/APs3JxB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAPs3JxB.png&h=b618d01d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T03:52:15.000Z","msg":"青春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d031d85bab335bbd716aa98f9502d551509491ad","tid":964033,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T03:58:28.000Z","msg":"殺死gay"},{"pid":"3698d0735d3d03b0f3c03e3ad927e56c239364e4","tid":964033,"uid":205704,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"d031d85bab335bbd716aa98f9502d551509491ad","tid":964033,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T03:58:28.000Z","msg":"殺死gay"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T04:00:32.000Z","msg":"拿嚕托"},{"pid":"720f98454e2c4a31a8e571b616d45a587637705a","tid":964033,"uid":86587,"like":4,"dislike":19,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T04:12:33.000Z","msg":"但是...我...我...『我不渴求語言，我想要的東西確實存在，那一定不是希望互相了解，希望友好相處，希望待在一起之類的事情，我並不想讓別人來理解我，而是想要去了解，想了解，想明白，想弄明白之後安心度日，想得到一份平靜，因為一無所知這一點讓我極其畏懼，想要完全理解什麼的，是一個極其自以為是、獨斷專行且傲慢的願望，真的很卑鄙，令人厭煩，懷有那種願望的自己簡直惡性到無可救藥。可是如果...如果，彼此都有這種想法的話，把那醜惡的自我滿足互相強加給對方，如果存在這種可以相容的關係的話...我了解那種事情是絕對辦不到的，也知道自己難以企及那樣的東西。即便如此...』即使如此我也...我也...我也想要真物。"},{"pid":"0c6c34c4ccc68c41390c6adf893673e99889906e","tid":964033,"uid":8726,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T04:21:52.000Z","msg":"當我舉起第二把劍....."},{"pid":"b016eed1f0520ecb5cdc86194e0f9c43491cc70e","tid":964033,"uid":125203,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T04:34:02.000Z","msg":"化物語13話 睇星星果段<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XqpxX4ltje4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXqpxX4ltje4&d=HoBoMebGnLthbdL9qGoKXwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=a25c8eee\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XqpxX4ltje4</a>"},{"pid":"fad530a200a5981e7d216aebf00454177db131da","tid":964033,"uid":46310,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T04:37:09.000Z","msg":"幫我撐10秒"},{"pid":"422474847aa00deb646389df42f03da41470a3cb","tid":964033,"uid":120064,"like":38,"dislike":4,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T04:40:21.000Z","msg":"就只差一步了！我現在還是處於「負數」狀態！我只想讓自己從「負數」回歸於「零」的狀態而已啊！<br />\n<br />\n呢句野可以套用係好多人身上，包括我"},{"pid":"58220f1484583d694a675672d3c538d06e6cea26","tid":964033,"uid":55511,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T04:43:01.000Z","msg":"勸樓主唔好睇太多大老師 早啲解脫"},{"pid":"049753a66ead950e24422ec6ace16c473705dc3f","tid":964033,"uid":43041,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T04:46:37.000Z","msg":"幫我撐十秒！！"},{"pid":"790f09ac24a2c01934fd9a45a63d85d96d4f281c","tid":964033,"uid":84043,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T04:47:50.000Z","msg":"大哥哥"},{"pid":"8